# =============================================================================
# Loon-Rules / AI.list
# 建议策略: AIGC（稳定支持 OpenAI/Claude 等的节点组）
# 格式: 无策略后缀；订阅时在 Loon 选择 policy=AIGC
# 维护: 改完 push → Loon 点更新订阅
# =============================================================================
#
# ## 来源（后续 AI 自动更新请优先拉取这些 URL 再合并去重）
#
# SOURCES:
# - OpenAI Network allowlist (官方)
#   https://help.openai.com/en/articles/9247338-network-recommendations-for-chatgpt-errors-on-web-and-apps
# - Tartarus2014 Loon AI.lsr
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Tartarus2014/Loon-Script/master/Rule/Other/AI.lsr
# - SukkaW / ruleset.skk.moe AIGC
#   https://ruleset.skk.moe/List/non_ip/ai.conf
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SukkaW/Surge/master/List/non_ip/ai.conf
# - blackmatrix7 OpenAI (社区常用，可选对照)
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script/master/rule/Loon/OpenAI/OpenAI.list
# - blackmatrix7 Claude
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script/master/rule/Loon/Claude/Claude.list
# - blackmatrix7 Gemini
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script/master/rule/Loon/Gemini/Gemini.list
# - xpdigital Apple-AI (Apple Intelligence；本列表末段收录核心项)
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/xpdigital/Apple-Rule/main/Apple-AI.list
# - beckyeeky Loon-Rules（本文件）
#   https://raw.githubusercontent.com/beckyeeky/Loon-Rules/main/rules/AI.list
#
# UPDATE_HINT:
# 1) curl 上述 raw/文档域列表
# 2) 抽取 DOMAIN / DOMAIN-SUFFIX / DOMAIN-KEYWORD / URL-REGEX 行
# 3) 去掉策略后缀与空行，按「厂商分段」合并；同域名保留一条
# 4) 保留本文件 SOURCES 头与分段注释
# 5) 不要对 AI 域名做 MitM 解密
#
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
